                   %IFNDEF           $PhoneVAR
$PhoneVAR          EQUATE            1
.
.
. Field Definitions
. -----------------
.
. Field            Type            Length    From - To        Description
.-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PhoneREC           RECORD
ContactID          dim               7        1 - 7
PhoneType          DIM               1        8 - 8     (From PhoneType include)
Use_Phone          FORM              1        9 - 9     (Use Customer Telephone)
Number             DIM               10      10 - 19
Filler2            DIM               1       20 - 20
Extension          DIM               7       21 - 27
Created            DIM               8       28 - 35
Date_Added         DIM               8       36 - 43
Date_Changed       DIM               8       44 - 51
User               DIM               10      52 - 61
AllowTexting       form              1
                   RECORDEND

TempPhoneREC       RECORD            LIKE       PhoneREC
OrigPhoneREC       RECORD            LIKE       PhoneREC
SavePhoneREC       RECORD            LIKE       PhoneREC
.
.
. File Keys and File Labels
. -------------------------
.
PhoneK1SIZE        CONST             "8"                                      //Length of the Key variable)
PhoneK2SIZE        CONST             "18"                                     //Length of the Key variable 2)
PhoneK3SIZE        CONST             "18"                                     //Length of the Key variable 3)
.
PhoneI1DEF         INIT              "-N,1-8"                                  (Index definitions for Key 1)
PhoneI2DEF         INIT              "-N,10-19,1-8"                            (Index definitions for Key 2)
PhoneI3DEF         INIT              "-N,8-8,10-19,1-7"                        (Index definitions for Key 2)
.
PhoneFileSize      CONST             "80"                                     //Length of each Record)

PhoneKY            DIM               PhoneK1SIZE                              //The Actual 'Key' variable)
PhoneKY2           DIM               PhoneK2SIZE                              //The Actual 'Key' variable)

PhonePROG          INIT              "Program Name"
